      "options": {
        "code": { "language": "plaintext", "showLineNumbers": false, "showMiniMap": false },
        "content": "## BlackBar Service Level Objectives\n\n| SLO | Target | SLI | Measurement Window |\n|-----|--------|-----|--------------------|\n| **Availability** | 99.9% | Successful requests / Total requests | 30 days rolling |\n| **Latency (P95)** | < 500ms | 95th percentile response time | 5 minutes |\n| **Latency (P99)** | < 2s | 99th percentile response time | 5 minutes |\n| **Error Rate** | < 1% | 5xx responses / Total responses | 5 minutes |\n| **AI Availability** | 99% | Successful LLM requests / Total LLM requests | 30 days rolling |\n\n### Error Budget Policy\n\n- **> 50% remaining**: Normal operations, deploy freely\n- **25-50% remaining**: Increased caution, limit risky deployments\n- **< 25% remaining**: Focus on reliability, freeze non-critical changes\n- **0% remaining**: Incident mode, all hands on reliability\n\n### Escalation\n\n- SLO breach for > 5 minutes: Alert to ops team\n- SLO breach for > 30 minutes: Page on-call engineer\n- Error budget < 25%: Weekly reliability review\n- Error budget exhausted: Postmortem required",
